Document: GLTFSkin
Path: godot/classes/class_gltfskin.rst
Summary: Represents a skin in a glTF file, defining how bones influence mesh vertices.

Inherits: Resource < RefCounted < Object

A skin in a glTF file, defining how bones influence mesh vertices. This resource is generated by the GLTFDocument importer.

The skin resource contains a list of joints (nodes that are bones) and a list of inverse bind matrices. The inverse bind matrices are used to transform vertices from model space to bone space.

Properties:
  joints (Array[NodePath]): The list of nodes that are bones.
  inverse_bind_matrices (Array[Transform3D]): The list of inverse bind matrices.
---CHUNK---
